metadata.name: Test Subject
metadata.description: By [P4SD](https://opensea.io/P4SD) https://psssdnft.com P4SD Labs has been experimenting on 10,000 willing Test Subjects in order to enhance their creativity. Unfortunately experiments have resulted in a major side effect, becoming Possessed! As a result, each Subject has become animated, constantly switching between two states, Blessed and Possessed. You can switch this on-chain, to what you feel represents you most.
